Wrote this today.. had a certain OCP member in mind..

I'm not sure what's going on
What's happening in my head
Situations and circumstances
Are not the same as what was said
You'd say one thing but do another
I'm sick of all your lies
You'd give me filth and force-feed anger
With your pitiful disguise
I gave you all I had to give
And still you took away
Any faith I ever had
That we wouldn't end up this way
Like a cancer you latched on and tore
Away my self-esteem
You warped my vision and stretched the truth
All you were was a bad dream
My crippled perception saw you as my true love
For some reason I thought it was true
Now I look back and I realize that
What's factual is I don't need you
Every day I'm alive I'll live with regret
For the time of my life I gave you
No matter how hard I try, I'll never forget
All of the pain I subdued
I can only hope you'll get on with your life
And seek help for your hurtful ways
Because although you hurt me, I can't help but care
And I will pray that your hatred won't stay
So please bear with me right now as I vent
And go over this whole ordeal
Because now that we're through I'm no longer afraid
To tell you just how I feel

You are the color red. You are the most
controversial of all the colors. You are often
easily angered, but as easily as you got
excited, you come down. When angered, do you
have the tendency to be malicious? Afterwards,
do you end up begging for forgiveness? Maybe.
But you're incredibly generous, and, odd
enough, needy. You love to hate, and
sometimes, you hate to love. This color
describes you as generally edgy. When in a bad
situation, you're pessimistic, and when you're
in a good situation, you're extremely
optimistic. You're painfully tempermental, and
sometimes it hurts the ones you love. But with
an exciting and stimulating attitude, you enjoy
talking to people and being social. But aside
from your bold and outgoing attitude, you're
attention-needing and attention-getting. This
color is associated with lust and desire--and
you are both lust and desirous. You're a
protective person when it comes to the people
you love. You're incredibly sharp-witted and
powerful (not to mention intelligent!).
